    <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:1.5pt 1.5pt 1.5pt 1.5pt'>
    <p class=3DMsoNormal><b><span =
style=3D'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:Arial;
    color:#333333'>Why are some of the gold stocks not breaking out with =
the
    price of Gold?</span></b><span =
style=3D'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:Arial;
    color:#333333'> </span></p>
